                     IPNS Proprietary Research Information


   [New IPNS logo.jpg] Companies may purchase beam time to do proprietary
   experiments by paying the full cost of the facility under a rate
   structure established by the U. S. Department of Energy. The current
   rate is approximately $5000/Instrument/Day. For information, contact
   the IPNS Division Director, Raymond Teller, at (630)252-4999.
